glish domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"robert Ingeram was born in 1174, in Cleveland, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom as the son of John Ingrim. He had at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"1174–":"1174–Surnud","1120–Male":"1120–Surnud","1138–1185":"1138–1185","1174–Male":"1174–Surnud","1165–Female":"1165–Surnud","1113–1170":"1113–1170","1138":"1138","1113":"1113","1165":"1165","1120":"1120","1174":"1174","1185":"1185","1170":"1170","North Riding, Yorkshire,England":"Cleveland, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1174–":"1174–Kuollut","1120–Male":"1120–Kuollut","1138–1185":"1138–1185","1174–Male":"1174–Kuollut","1165–Female":"1165–Kuollut","1113–1170":"1113–1170","1138":"1138","1113":"1113","1165":"1165","1120":"1120","1174":"1174","1185":"1185","1170":"1170","North Riding, Yorkshire,England":"Cleveland, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1174–":"1174–Décédé","1120–Male":"1120–Décédé","1138–1185":"1138–1185","1174–Male":"1174–Décédé","1165–Female":"1165–Décédée","1113–1170":"1113–1170","1138":"1138","1113":"1113","1165":"1165","1120":"1120","1174":"1174","1185":"1185","1170":"1170","North Riding, Yorkshire,England":"Cleveland, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"robert Ingeram est né en 1174, à Cleveland, Everwyck, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fils de John Ingrim. Il a eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"1174–":"1174–Verstorben","1120–Male":"1120–Verstorben","1138–1185":"1138–1185","1174–Male":"1174–Verstorben","1165–Female":"1165–Verstorben","1113–1170":"1113–1170","1138":"1138","1113":"1113","1165":"1165","1120":"1120","1174":"1174","1185":"1185","1170":"1170","North Riding, Yorkshire,England":"Cleveland, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"robert Ingeram wurde 1174 in Cleveland, Yorkshire, England, United Kingdom, als Sohn von John I